              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='color:#9CA3AF;font-size:14px;'>AtmaSphere quietly powers the agents and interactions across the Vireoka ecosystem, including:</p><ul style='color:#9CA3AF;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;'><li>AI-guided communication and debate coaching</li><li>Memoir and coffee-table book creation</li><li>Niche dating and relationship platforms</li><li>Cloud cost and architecture optimization</li><li>Creative and strategic workflows for founders and teams</li><li>Emerging financial experiences, including quantum-secure stablecoin rails</li></ul>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
